Excel Assignment 5



 
1. How many types of conditions are available in conditional formatting on Excel? 
Ans; There are many type are available in conditional formatting 
Higlight cell rule 
top/bottom rules 
data bars 
colour scale 
and many more 


 
2. How to insert border in Excel with Format Cells dialog? 
Ans;  Just go to format cell and format the border of the cell as per requirement.


 
3. How to Format Numbers as Currency in Excel? 
Ans ; Press Ctrl+1 for formatting then go to currency and choose the currency as per requirement .



 
4. What are the steps to format numbers in Excel with the Percent style? 
Ans ; First select the range and click ctrl+1 and get number formatting and after that go to custom tab and type 0\% and get the data into percentage style .




 
5. What is a shortcut to merge two or more cells in excel? 
Ans ;Select the cells, Click the Alt+H+M and after seclect M then this way I can merge .


 
6. How do you use text commands in Excel? 

Ans ; Text command generally use for manipulate the text data using formula 
First make = and after that we can perform many of the text command 
like concatenate , left , right , proper , upper , lower and so on
one of them =concatenate (text1,text2) and hit enter for adding two text.

